# SaverSonic - Deal Sharing Network

SaverSonic (saversonic.com) is a dynamic deal-sharing platform that connects users with the best online deals and discounts. Built with modern web technologies, it enables users to discover, share, and interact with deals across various categories.

## Core Features
- Deal posting and sharing
- User following system
- Deal following/bookmarking
- Interactive comments on deals
- Direct links to deal websites
- Real-time updates using WebSockets

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend**: Nuxt 3 (Vue.js framework) inside the folder my-nuxt-app
- **Backend**: Express.js inside the folder backend
- **State Management**: Pinia
- **Real-time Features**: WebSocket integration
- **Architecture**: Full-stack JavaScript application

SaverSonic creates a community-driven ecosystem where users can discover savings opportunities while engaging with like-minded deal seekers. The platform emphasizes user interaction and real-time updates to ensure deals are always current and relevant.